1
00:00:06,060 --> 00:00:09,980
=Menyatukan Hidup dan Mati=

2
00:00:10,060 --> 00:00:11,980
=Episod 17=

3
00:00:26,030 --> 00:00:28,270
Kasihanilah, tuan yang baik! Kasihanilah!

4
00:00:30,640 --> 00:00:31,320
Buka mata anda.

5
00:00:31,320 --> 00:00:34,000
Saya tahu bagaimana ini berlaku. Saya akan dibungkam sebaik sahaja saya melihat wajah anda.

6
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:35,310
Saya tidak melihat apa-apa!

7
00:00:36,560 --> 00:00:37,700
Adakah saya tidak jelas?

8
00:00:38,235 --> 00:00:39,239
Tuan.

9
00:00:39,240 --> 00:00:40,540
Itu agak berlebihan.

10
00:00:41,080 --> 00:00:42,660
Tolong buka mata anda.

11
00:00:42,751 --> 00:00:43,669
Kami membawa anda ke sini

12
00:00:43,670 --> 00:00:45,110
hanya untuk anda memberi keterangan.

13
00:00:49,960 --> 00:00:51,150
Dengan senang hati.

14
00:00:54,839 --> 00:00:56,150
Lelaki yang baik.

15
00:01:14,950 --> 00:01:16,932
(Di Rumah Zhao)

16
00:01:16,933 --> 00:01:19,190
Sakitnya!

17
00:01:20,111 --> 00:01:21,119
Ayah!

18
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:24,010
Bawa Ma San ke sini sekarang!

19
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:25,230
Inilah tempatnya.

20
00:01:30,030 --> 00:01:30,980
Buka pintu!

21
00:01:32,148 --> 00:01:33,470
Buka!

22
00:01:35,630 --> 00:01:36,620
Inilah orangnya.

23
00:01:38,257 --> 00:01:39,260
Di sana!

24
00:01:40,220 --> 00:01:41,159
Tuan Song!

25
00:01:41,160 --> 00:01:42,199
Ini saya, Tuan Song!

26
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:42,799
Saya tahu.

27
00:01:42,800 --> 00:01:43,909
Kenapa kamu di sini lagi?

28
00:01:43,910 --> 00:01:44,496
Ini saya!

29
00:01:44,497 --> 00:01:45,719
Kamu kenal Tuan Song?

30
00:01:45,720 --> 00:01:46,721
Sudah tentu.

31
00:01:46,722 --> 00:01:47,790
Tuan Song! Tolong...

32
00:01:48,373 --> 00:01:49,750
- Jangan masuk!
- Biarkan kami masuk!

33
00:01:50,075 --> 00:01:51,020
Tuan Song!

34
00:01:53,471 --> 00:01:54,580
Tuan Song!

35
00:01:54,708 --> 00:01:55,996
Jauhkan diri!

36
00:01:57,522 --> 00:01:58,729
Kamu tidak membunuh saya kali terakhir,

37
00:01:58,730 --> 00:02:00,438
dan sekarang kamu bawa bantuan!

38
00:02:00,439 --> 00:02:02,389
- Apa yang menyebabkan reaksi ini?
- Kamu!

39
00:02:02,875 --> 00:02:03,549
Tuan Song!

40
00:02:03,550 --> 00:02:04,900
Jauhkan diri dari saya!

41
00:02:05,370 --> 00:02:05,994
Tolong!

42
00:02:05,995 --> 00:02:07,020
Tuan Song!

43
00:02:11,750 --> 00:02:14,100
Tuan, pernahkah tuan merasakan perasaan itu

44
00:02:14,671 --> 00:02:16,950
di mana tuan tahu tuan terlupa sesuatu,

45
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:20,799
tetapi tuan tidak dapat mengenal pasti apa sebenarnya?

46
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,790
Apa sebenarnya yang tuan terlupa?

47
00:02:23,035 --> 00:02:24,340
Ia seperti...

48
00:02:25,910 --> 00:02:27,590
Adakah tuan mengarahkan saya untuk melakukan sesuatu?

49
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:31,129
- Berhenti mengejar saya!
- Berhenti berlari!

50
00:02:31,130 --> 00:02:32,881
- Berhenti mengejar saya!
- Awak berhenti berlari dahulu.

51
00:02:32,882 --> 00:02:35,100
Adakah tuan memerlukan bantuan saya?

52
00:02:36,810 --> 00:02:37,872
Tembak!

53
00:02:38,315 --> 00:02:39,079
Tuan.

54
00:02:39,080 --> 00:02:40,909
Saya terlupa tuan meminta saya pergi

55
00:02:40,910 --> 00:02:41,950
ke kediaman Tuan Song.

56
00:02:41,951 --> 00:02:43,180
Tuan terlupa?

57
00:02:43,573 --> 00:02:44,452
Maksud saya, mereka rapat.

58
00:02:44,453 --> 00:02:45,478
Mereka tidak akan...

59
00:02:45,479 --> 00:02:46,740
Pergi sekarang!

60
00:02:46,910 --> 00:02:47,620
Qiu!

61
00:02:47,750 --> 00:02:48,820
Jalan yang salah.

62
00:02:49,080 --> 00:02:50,260
Ya, tuan!

63
00:02:50,750 --> 00:02:51,320
Berhenti!

64
00:02:51,320 --> 00:02:54,339
- Jika awak berhenti mengejar, saya akan berhenti berlari!
- Kenapa awak berlari pada mulanya?

65
00:02:54,339 --> 00:02:56,680
- Saya akan berhenti berlari.
- Saya akan berhenti mengejar. Tuan Song!

66
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:57,439
Awak... Awak penipu!

67
00:02:57,440 --> 00:02:59,070
Saya tahu saya tidak boleh mempercayai awak!

68
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:07,600
(Malam tadi,
ubat Zhao Tai habis kesannya.)

69
00:03:07,600 --> 00:03:09,860
(Nasib baik, dia bangun untuk makan sesuatu
di tengah malam.)

70
00:03:09,860 --> 00:03:11,120
(Saya campurkan semua ubat ke dalam makanannya.)

71
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:13,510
Adakah saya akan tinggal untuk makan malam? Tidak, terima kasih.

72
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:25,590
(Cik Lichun...)

73
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:28,150
(Dia memegang tangan saya...)

74
00:03:50,990 --> 00:03:52,879
Berhenti berlari...

75
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:54,310
Berhenti mengejar saya...

76
00:03:54,990 --> 00:03:56,319
Berhenti berlari...

77
00:03:56,320 --> 00:03:57,439
Saya akan berhenti...

78
00:03:57,440 --> 00:03:58,620
Dengar...

79
00:03:58,830 --> 00:04:01,430
Jika kamu mengejar saya lagi,
Encik Ma akan muncul!

80
00:04:02,630 --> 00:04:05,820
Tidak mungkin.
Encik Ma pergi ke rumah majistret.

81
00:04:06,190 --> 00:04:08,189
Dia tidak akan datang.

82
00:04:08,190 --> 00:04:10,950
Kamu menipu saya, ya?

83
00:04:11,190 --> 00:04:12,263
Baiklah.

84
00:04:12,264 --> 00:04:14,947
Bunuh saya jika perlu!

85
00:04:14,948 --> 00:04:16,169
Saya tidak boleh berlari lagi...

86
00:04:16,170 --> 00:04:17,580
Bunuh kamu?

87
00:04:18,613 --> 00:04:19,514
Apa?

88
00:04:19,515 --> 00:04:21,230
Encik Ma suruh saya datang ke sini.

89
00:04:21,510 --> 00:04:23,159
Dia kata saya perlu memberi keterangan

90
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,199
dan meminta kamu

91
00:04:24,200 --> 00:04:25,550
menulis kenyataan.

92
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:27,039
Betul?

93
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:27,989
Betul.

94
00:04:27,990 --> 00:04:28,830
Apa?

95
00:04:29,588 --> 00:04:31,574
Adakah kamu tidak menerima mesej daripada Qiu?

96
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:33,390
Tiada siapa beritahu saya apa-apa!

97
00:04:37,311 --> 00:04:38,852
Kamu orang gila!

98
00:04:38,853 --> 00:04:41,340
Kenapa kamu tidak katakan itu lebih awal?

99
00:04:45,510 --> 00:04:46,670
Sila ikut sini.

100
00:04:47,990 --> 00:04:49,140
Magistrat Zhao.

101
00:04:50,070 --> 00:04:50,879
Anda minta untuk berjumpa dengan saya?

102
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:52,020
Encik Ma, anda di sini.

103
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:53,199
Kamu budak nakal!

104
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:55,300
Encik Ma ada di sini! Beritahu yang sebenar sekarang!

105
00:05:02,070 --> 00:05:03,420
Tai!

106
00:05:04,640 --> 00:05:07,829
Tai! Kau telah meninggalkan dunia ini terlalu cepat!

107
00:05:07,830 --> 00:05:09,860
Jangan tinggalkan aku...

108
00:05:10,390 --> 00:05:11,390
Ayah.

109
00:05:12,790 --> 00:05:15,389
Saya cuma ada sesuatu dalam fikiran.

110
00:05:15,390 --> 00:05:17,020
Kenapa kamu begitu gelisah?

111
00:05:17,070 --> 00:05:19,270
Kamu menakutkan saya!

112
00:05:21,110 --> 00:05:22,270
Cakap.

113
00:05:23,790 --> 00:05:26,550
Ia berlaku kira-kira dua bulan lalu.

114
00:05:28,230 --> 00:05:29,269
Jiao.

115
00:05:29,270 --> 00:05:30,669
Mari, minum!

116
00:05:30,670 --> 00:05:31,950
Minum habis!

117
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:34,583
Mari kita minum bersama!

118
00:05:34,584 --> 00:05:35,807
Bersulang!

119
00:05:38,440 --> 00:05:40,789
Apa masalahnya, Encik Zhao?

120
00:05:40,790 --> 00:05:41,989
Apa lagi?

121
00:05:41,990 --> 00:05:43,949
Ia Song Yuan itu!

122
00:05:43,950 --> 00:05:45,599
Dia seperti anjing gila!

123
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:48,860
Dia tidak akan biarkan Encik Zhao sendirian!

124
00:05:48,880 --> 00:05:50,669
Dia tidak berputus asa.

125
00:05:50,670 --> 00:05:53,620
Song Yuan telah berlari ke seluruh bandar,

126
00:05:53,790 --> 00:05:57,340
mengumpul setiap butiran tentang perbuatan masa lalu kamu.

127
00:05:59,510 --> 00:06:00,829
Selepas semua kekecohan itu,

128
00:06:00,830 --> 00:06:02,880
Saya tidak boleh menikmati diri saya lagi apabila saya di sini.

129
00:06:03,950 --> 00:06:04,549
Tong.

130
00:06:04,550 --> 00:06:06,030
Jangan marah. Mari.

131
00:06:06,031 --> 00:06:07,523
Mari kita berseronok.

132
00:06:07,550 --> 00:06:09,759
Encik Zhao, jangan risau sangat.

133
00:06:09,760 --> 00:06:10,879
Song Yuan mungkin

134
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:13,599
berlari ke seluruh bandar, tetapi dia tidak akan sampai di sini.

135
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:14,389
Selain itu,

136
00:06:14,390 --> 00:06:18,180
kita mempunyai teman yang sangat berharga di sini.

137
00:06:23,670 --> 00:06:24,900
Emas?

138
00:06:26,440 --> 00:06:28,670
Bagaimana jika saya berjaya membawa Song Yuan ke sini?

139
00:06:31,390 --> 00:06:34,390
Itu hebat! Sangat hebat!

140
00:06:37,070 --> 00:06:37,989
Ayuh!

141
00:06:37,990 --> 00:06:39,639
Mari kita semua angkat gelas untuk Encik Zhao.

142
00:06:39,640 --> 00:06:40,599
Di sini, di sini!

143
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:41,580
Sorakan!

144
00:06:51,270 --> 00:06:52,580
Ya ampun!

145
00:06:52,670 --> 00:06:56,670
Siapa pemuda tampan ini?

146
00:06:59,510 --> 00:07:01,300
Apa pendapat kamu? Tidak buruk, kan?

147
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:04,180
Saya hampir tidak mengenali kamu.

148
00:07:06,366 --> 00:07:07,710
Adakah ini orangnya?

149
00:07:08,640 --> 00:07:09,879
Encik Zhao meminta saya

150
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:12,879
membuatkan dia topeng dari kulit manusia.

151
00:07:12,880 --> 00:07:15,670
Yang terbakar teruk.

152
00:07:16,110 --> 00:07:17,830
Topeng kulit manusia?

153
00:07:18,640 --> 00:07:20,069
Kepakaran saya terkenal

154
00:07:20,070 --> 00:07:21,303
di merata tempat.

155
00:07:21,304 --> 00:07:22,779
Sebaik sahaja kamu memakai topeng itu,

156
00:07:22,780 --> 00:07:25,180
ibu kamu sendiri pun tidak akan mengenali kamu.
